 | SYSLIB0055 | `AdvSimd.ShiftRightLogicalRoundedNarrowingSaturate*` signed overloads | Unsigned overloads |
 | SYSLIB0056 | `Assembly.LoadFrom` with `AssemblyHashAlgorithm` | Overloads without `AssemblyHashAlgorithm` |

